room_title: Escape room "The Mafia" by Insomnia Escape Room DC in Washington, D.C.
room_description: Bootleggers, La Cosa Nostra, federal agents and high-rank DC politicians, mixed in a strong cocktail of fun and intellectual challenge. This is the year 1933, under mysterious circumstances, you are transferred to a secret speakeasy, back in the waning days of Prohibition.
